  "introduction": "<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Josué 12 na <em><a href=\"https://www.die-bibel.de/en/bible/BHS/JOS.12\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Biblia Hebraica Stuttgartensia</a></em></p>\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\"><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QVg_CVW6M0A\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Comentário a Josué 12,1-6</a></p>\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\"><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xWGZqYwl_zI\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Comentário a Josué 12,7-8</a></p>\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\"><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aRhBRxwhZwQ\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Comentário a Josué 12,9-24</a></p>\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\"><strong><mark class=\"has-inline-color has-vivid-red-color\" style=\"background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0)\">Aviso</mark></strong>: nas notas de rodapé, clique no link ativo para acessar as referências bíblicas.</p>\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">_________________________________________________________________________________________________________</p>",
  "verses": [
    {
      "number": 1,
      "text": "E esses. Os reis da terra. Que fazem ferir os filhos de Yisra’el. E possuem eles a terra deles. No passadouro. do Yarden. Desde o levante do sol. Desde o varzeado de ‘Arnon. Até o monte de Hermon. E o total da ‘arabah. Desde levante.",
      "lines": [
        {
          "line_index": 0,
          "text": "E esses.",
          "raw_html": "<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\"> E esses<a name=\"rf1-18456\"></a><sup><a href=\"#fn1-18456\" rel=\"footnote\" title=\"Clique para ir para a nota de rodapé 1\">1</a></sup>.</p>"
        },
        {
          "line_index": 1,
          "text": "Os reis da terra.",
          "raw_html": "<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Os reis da terra.</p>"
        },
